### 5. 개발 패턴 및 컨벤션

#### 5.1 계층별 역할

| 계층 | 위치 | 역할 |
|------|------|------|
| GraphQL Controller | `graphql/controller/` | 요청 수신, 응답 조합, `@PreAuthorize` |
| GraphQL Service | `graphql/service/` | `@GrpcClient`로 gRPC 호출 |
| gRPC Service | `{module}/controller/` | gRPC 요청 수신, Service 호출 |
| Service | `{module}/service/` | 비즈니스 로직, `@Transactional` |
| Repository | `domain/repository/` | DB 접근 (JPA) |

#### 5.2 개발 순서 (Tidy First 원칙)

1. **Entity 정의** → `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/user/`
2. **Repository 작성** → `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/user/`
3. **GraphQL Schema** → `graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/`
4. **Proto 정의** → `protobuf/src/main/proto/user/`
5. **Service 구현** → `{module}/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/`
6. **gRPC Service** → `{module}/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/`
7. **GraphQL Service** → `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/`
8. **GraphQL Controller** → `graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/`

#### 5.3 테스트 패턴

```kotlin
// 서비스 단위 테스트 (user/src/test/kotlin/...)
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension::class)
class UserServiceTest {
    @Mock
    private lateinit var repository: UserRepository

    @InjectMocks
    private lateinit var service: UserService

    @Test
    fun `should update user profile`() {
        // given
        val userId = "test-user-id"
        val user = UserEntity(id = userId, phoneNumber = "010-xxxx-xxxx")
        `when`(repository.findById(userId)).thenReturn(Optional.of(user))

        // when
        val result = service.updateProfile(userId, nickname = "newName")

        // then
        assertThat(result.nickname).isEqualTo("newName")
        verify(repository).save(user)
    }
}
```

